    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m selling my car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs smoothly and looks great. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty won't let you down. Come by and take it for a test drive\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
