    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the adaptive cruise control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a complete service history and a recent multi-point inspection. It has recently received a fresh oil change, new cabin filters, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. It delivers a quiet, composed ride with no unusual noises or vibrations. This is a turn-key car for a buyer who values a well-documented history and a clean, reliable presentation.",
